('Richard & Amy Fish (YWAM Tyler)', 'individual', 'richardandamyfish.com', 'Long-term YWAM Tyler staff couple leading DTS and serving in Media Communications at the Twin Oaks campus; maintain a dedicated personal ministry site with giving instructions (online + mail-in). | Field: Twin Oaks campus, Garden Valley, TX (YWAM Tyler) — media com | Comms: Active blog/site at richardandamyfish.com and blog.ywamtyler.org/autho', 8, 'Individual couple, US base, active personal giving page, Christian training-ministry role, clear support-raising language.', 'hunter:ywam-bases', 'pending', '{"h": "ywam-bases", "src": "https://richardandamyfish.com/"}'::jsonb),('Mark & Janet Baxter (YWAM Jacksonville)', 'individual', 'ywamjax.org/staff', 'Founded YWAM Jacksonville in 2001; Mark is Base Director and North American Regional Leader for YWAM Frontier Missions, Janet is Administrative Director; 25 years on personal support. | Field: Jacksonville, FL, plus international frontier missions work  | Comms: Not confirmed — base donate page active at ywamjax.org/donate', 7, 'Long-tenured individual missionary couple, US base, Christian, base-level donate page allows designating gifts to specific staff.', 'hunter:ywam-bases', 'pending', '{"h": "ywam-bases", "src": "https://ywamjax.org/staff/"}'::jsonb),('David & Abigail Elliott (YWAM Honolulu)', 'individual', 'elliottmissions.wordpress.com/prayinggiving', 'Missionary couple with a dedicated WordPress giving/prayer page; checks payable to YWAM Honolulu, also accept PayPal. | Field: Kapolei, HI (YWAM Honolulu), with a Houston connection (davi | Comms: Not confirmed — site is active', 6, 'Individual couple with personal support page, Christian, US-based; base affiliation slightly ambiguous (Honolulu address, Houston email) so worth confirming.', 'hunter:ywam-bases', 'pending', '{"h": "ywam-bases", "src": "https://elliottmissions.wordpress.com/prayinggiving/"}'::jsonb),('Melissa Richardson (YWAM Salem)', 'individual', 'ywamsalem.org/staff-support', 'On YWAM Salem staff since 2016 (DTS in Germany, 2012); directs Mission Adventures, the base''''s junior-high/high-school summer program. | Field: Salem, OR — Director of Mission Adventures (summer camp mini | Comms: Not confirmed — listed on active ywamsalem.org/staff-support giving pa', 7, 'Named individual staff member on a base-run personal-support giving platform; Christian, US base, clear ongoing role.', 'hunter:ywam-bases', 'pending', '{"h": "ywam-bases", "src": "https://www.ywamsalem.org/staff-support"}'::jsonb),('Jessica Miller (YWAM Lancaster)', 'individual', 'ywamlancaster.com/missionary/jessica-miller', 'Joined YWAM Lancaster staff August 2022; personal missionary bio page on the base site tied into the base''''s Peer Partner giving program. | Field: Lancaster, PA base staff; prior field experience in Ensenada | Comms: Not confirmed', 7, 'Individual staff member with dedicated bio/support page on a US base site with an active monthly-giving mechanism (Peer Partner).', 'hunter:ywam-bases', 'pending', '{"h": "ywam-bases", "src": "https://www.ywamlancaster.com/missionary/jessica-miller/"}'::jsonb),('Anna James (YWAM Lancaster)', 'individual', 'ywamlancaster.com/missionary/anna-james', 'Called to YWAM Lancaster staff after completing DTS with YWAM Orlando; has an individual missionary bio/support page on the base site. | Field: Lancaster, PA base staff; DTS completed at YWAM Orlando | Comms: Not confirmed', 6, 'Individual staff member on active US base giving platform; limited bio detail available.', 'hunter:ywam-bases', 'pending', '{"h": "ywam-bases", "src": "https://www.ywamlancaster.com/missionary/anna-james/"}'::jsonb),('Wilna Jean (YWAM Lancaster)', 'individual', 'ywamlancaster.com/missionary/wilna-jean', 'Serves as a teacher at YWAM Lancaster''''s Hub Learning Center; has an individual missionary bio/support page. | Field: Lancaster, PA base staff — teacher at the Hub Learning Cente | Comms: Not confirmed', 6, 'Individual staff member on active US base giving platform; limited bio detail available.', 'hunter:ywam-bases', 'pending', '{"h": "ywam-bases", "src": "https://www.ywamlancaster.com/missionary/wilna-jean/"}'::jsonb),('Brian & Liz Hebert (FBMI)', 'individual', 'fbmi.org/missionary/hebert', 'FBMI missionaries church-planting in the Greater Toronto Area alongside veteran missionary Brian Johnston; documented extensive deputation travel (TN, FL, IL, KS, TX, WY, CO and more) before reaching the field; recent letter "Reach the World" on Bible distribu | Field: Toronto, Canada | Comms: 2026 prayer letter ("Reach the World")', 6, 'Recently off deputation and still building/broadening its US donor base for an urban Canadian church plant — active prayer-letter writer.', 'hunter:prayer-letters', 'pending', '{"h": "prayer-letters", "src": "https://fbmi.org/missionary/hebert"}'::jsonb),('Lawrence & Tammy Williams (FBMI)', 'individual', 'fbmi.org/author/lawrence-williams', 'Former FBMI Team Ghana missionaries now planting Cimarron Fundamental Baptist Church stateside; multiple 2026 letters ("Believers, Baptisms, and Bibles," "Soul-Winning Opportunities," "Birthing of Cimarron Fundamental Baptist Church") describing Bible giveaway | Field: USA (Cimarron church plant; formerly FBMI Team Ghana) | Comms: 2026 prayer letter ("Believers, Baptisms, and Bibles")', 6, 'Active US-based church planter with a high-frequency prayer-letter cadence and individual-donor support model.', 'hunter:prayer-letters', 'pending', '{"h": "prayer-letters", "src": "https://fbmi.org/author/lawrence-williams"}'::jsonb),('Brian (BJ) & Arezoo Nibbe Jr (BIMI)', 'individual', 'bimi.org/content/abDeputation.php', 'BIMI missionaries to Romania, currently listed on BIMI''''s furlough/deputation roster as of July 2026, actively raising support. | Field: Romania | Comms: Listed active on BIMI deputation roster, July 2026', 8, 'Currently on BIMI''''s active deputation/furlough list — textbook hot lead raising individual-donor support right now.', 'hunter