/missionaries/behmanT.php"}'::jsonb),('Trent & Stephanie Granger (BIMI)', 'individual', 'bimi.org/missionaries/grangerT.php', 'BIMI missionaries to Mexico; completed a first term (two churches planted, two children born) but returned to the US for a daughter''''s health crisis, and are now preparing to return to deputation and back to Mexico. | Field: Mexico | Comms: Preparing to resume deputation (recent update, year not specified)', 8, 'About to re-enter active deputation/support-raising after a health-related furlough — strong near-term hot lead.', 'hunter:prayer-letters', 'pending', '{"h": "prayer-letters", "src": "https://www.bimi.org/missionaries/grangerT.php"}'::jsonb),('Robert & Rebekah Mach (BIMI)', 'individual', 'bimi.org/missionaries/machR.php', 'Veteran BIMI missionaries serving Anyama, Côte d''''Ivoire since 1995 (Fundamental Baptist Church and Institute of Anyama); currently listed on BIMI''''s "Missionaries on Furlough" page. | Field: Côte d''''Ivoire (Ivory Coast) | Comms: Listed on BIMI furlough roster', 6, 'Long-tenured individually-supported missionaries currently on furlough — actively reconnecting with US supporting churches.', 'hunter:prayer-letters', 'pending', '{"h": "prayer-letters", "src": "https://www.bimi.org/missionaries/machR.php"}'::jsonb),('Kyler J. & Emily K. Kerr (BIMI)', 'individual', 'bimi.org/pages/missionary/1669', 'BIMI missionaries #1669 headed to Zambia; Kyler first connected to the field on a 2014 missions trip that included bush ministry and Bible conferences; Emily is from Big Spring, TX. | Field: Zambia | Comms: Not specified in available excerpt', 7, 'BIMI missionary couple building a Zambia ministry with an individual US-donor support base.', 'hunter:prayer-letters', 'pending', '{"h": "prayer-letters", "src": "https://www.bimi.org/pages/missionary/1669"}'::jsonb),('Daniel & Raquel Akuokoh (BIMI)', 'individual', 'bimi.org/missionaries/akuokohD.php', 'BIMI missionaries married July 2018; Daniel is a Commonwealth Baptist C