e | Rev: Not found on ProPublica (founded 2021, likely small/early-st', 6, 'Founder-led, small/early-stage, prison and reentry niche match in Texas, though financial verification is incomplete', 'hunter:small-ministries2', 'pending', '{"h": "small-ministries2", "src": "https://worthypeople.org/about/"}'::jsonb),('Coalition of Churches in Prison Ministry (COCIPM)', 'organization', 'cocipm.org', 'North Texas coalition of churches sharing the Gospel with incarcerated individuals | Comms: Active North Texas Giving Day campaign presence | Rev: Not confirmed via ProPublica in available search results', 6, 'Explicit all-individual-donor funding model and prison-ministry niche match; revenue figure needs confirmation', 'hunter:small-ministries2', 'pending', '{"h": "small-ministries2", "src": "https://www.cocipm.org/about-us"}'::jsonb),('Joined To HaShem', 'organization', 'joinedtohashem.org', 'Messianic/Hebraic-perspective teaching ministry uplifting Yeshua as Messiah, reaching ~3,000 people weekly via email/livestream | Comms: Weekly teachings via email/livestream (ongoing) | Rev: $202k revenue / $170k expenses (2024, ProPublica); $147k (20', 6, 'Small revenue, individual-donor funded, closest match found to the Jewish-evangelism niche, though named leader not confirmed', 'hunter:small-ministries2', 'pending', '{"h": "small-ministries2", "src": "http://www.joinedtohashem.org/partner.html"}'::jsonb),('ICCM Life Center ("Changing Our City")', 'organization', 'changingourcity.org', 'Inner-city Minneapolis urban ministry offering outreach, recovery support groups, tutoring, mentoring, and GED courses | Comms: Not confirmed | Rev: Not confirmed via ProPublica in available search results', 6, 'Named founders, personal/grassroots origin story fits individual-donor model, Midwest inner-city niche match, but revenue unverified', 'hunter:small-ministries2', 'pending', '{"h": "small-ministries2", "src": "https://www.changingourcity.org/our-beginnings"}'::jsonb),('Loving Houston Foste