hing regular public newsletters; multi-generational missionary family (daughter Bethany Bridges is also an IPHC missionary). | Comms: Newsletter, February 2026', 7, 'February 2026 newsletter; IPHC missionaries raise personal support via individual giving pages at give.iphc.org.', 'hunter:active-bloggers', 'pending', '{"h": "active-bloggers", "src": "https://iphc.org/missions/presley-newsletter-february-2026/"}'::jsonb),('The Bambas (IPHC World Missions)', 'individual', 'iphc.org/missions/bamba-newsletter-february-2026', 'Bamba family | IPHC missionary couple serving in Japan, publishing regular newsletters to their supporter base. | Field: Japan | Comms: Newsletter, February 2026', 7, 'February 2026 newsletter; personally supported denominational missionaries with US donors via give.iphc.org.', 'hunter:active-bloggers', 'pending', '{"h": "active-bloggers", "src": "https://iphc.org/missions/bamba-newsletter-february-2026/"}'::jsonb),('Matt & Femke Helland (IPHC World Missions)', 'individual', 'iphc.org/missions/hellands-newsletter-february-2026', 'Matt & Femke Helland | IPHC missionary couple serving in Holland, sending regular ministry newsletters to supporters. | Field: Netherlands | Comms: Newsletter, February 2026', 7, 'February 2026 newsletter; support-raised US-sent missionaries in Europe — active communicators.', 'hunter:active-bloggers', 'pending', '{"h": "active-bloggers", "src": "https://iphc.org/missions/hellands-newsletter-february-2026/"}'::jsonb),('The Gonzales Family (IPHC World Missions)', 'individual', 'iphc.org/missions/gonzales-newsletter-february-2026', 'Gonzales family | IPHC missionaries in Thailand building a children''''s home, reporting progress to supporters through regular newsletters. | Field: Thailand | Comms: Newsletter, February 2026', 7, 'February 2026 newsletter with active project fundraising toward individual donors.', 'hunter:active-bloggers', 'pending', '{"h": "active-bloggers", "src": "https://iphc.org/missions/gonzales-newslette