('Thad & Nikki Roller (Free Methodist World Missions)', 'individual', 'give.fmcusa.org/donation/Thad_NikkiRoller', 'Thad & Nikki Roller | Free Methodist missionary family in Cajicá, Colombia training pastors and church planters across Colombia, Guatemala, and Mexico; personal FMC giving page; newsletters distributed via sending church (Wilmore FMC). | Field: Cajicá (Bogotá area), Colombia | Comms: Newsletter via Wilmore FMC missionary newsletters page, 2025-2026', 8, 'Personal giving page plus current newsletters listed on their supporting church''''s missionary-newsletter page; family with kids on the field.', 'hunter:active-bloggers', 'pending', '{"h": "active-bloggers", "src": "https://give.fmcusa.org/donation/Thad_NikkiRoller"}'::jsonb),('Dan & Hope Owsley (Free Methodist World Missions)', 'individual', 'give.fmcusa.org/owsley', 'Dan & Hope Owsley | Free Methodist missionaries with 30+ years in Brazil, moving from Brasília to São Paulo (Feb 2026) to serve the FM Bible Seminary; personal FMC giving page and church-distributed newsletters. | Field: São Paulo, Brazil | Comms: Newsletter via Wilmore FMC page announcing Feb 2026 move to São Paulo', 7, 'Active newsletter communicators in a fresh ministry transition (Feb 2026 move) — transition seasons spike donor communication needs.', 'hunter:active-bloggers', 'pending', '{"h": "active-bloggers", "src": "https://give.fmcusa.org/owsley"}'::jsonb),('Eduardo & Cindi Angelo (Free Methodist)', 'individual', 'wilmorefmc.org/resources/missionary-newsletters', 'Eduardo & Cindi Angelo | Pastors and church planters in Lisbon, Portugal supported by US Free Methodist churches and individuals; newsletters distributed through Wilmore FMC. | Field: Lisbon, Portugal | Comms: Newsletter via Wilmore FMC missionary newsletters page, 2025-2026', 7, 'Church planters in secular Europe with US supporter base and current newsletters on their sending church''''s page.', 'hunter:active-bloggers', 'pending', '{"h": "active-bloggers", "src": "h