ssionary-style support page on Reliant (reliant.org/raph.peters), meaning he raises personal support from individual donors while pastoring a young plant; named planter with act', 'hunter:church-planters', 'pending', '{"h": "church-planters", "src": "https://reliant.org/raph.peters"}'::jsonb),('Branches Church SF', 'individual', 'woodfincrew.com', 'Jake Woodfin | Jake and Hali Woodfin moved to San Francisco in 2019 as independent Baptist church-planting missionaries and launched Branches Church in the Sunset District (grand opening September 2021); woodfincrew.com is their personal planter site. | Field: Sunset District, San Francisco, Californ | Comms: YouTube ''''Woodfin San Francisco Church Plant Update'''' (January 2025) and blog upda', 8, 'Deputation-model planters whose blog explicitly covers ''''life during support raising''''; they continue raising individual missionary support for planting in one of America''''s most expensive cities, wit', 'hunter:church-planters', 'pending', '{"h": "church-planters", "src": "https://woodfincrew.com/"}'::jsonb),('Valley Church (Boston)', 'individual', 'namb.net/news/church-planting-class-of-2025-marks-highest-number-of-new-plants-since-2016', 'Jacob Ambrose | Sent by Temple Baptist Church (Ruston, LA), Jacob Ambrose completed a Send Network residency at Redemption Hill Church in Medford and launched Valley Church in 2025 as part of Send Network''''s ''''Class of 2025''''. | Field: Greater Boston (Medford area), Massachus | Comms: Featured in NAMB/Baptist Press ''''Class of 2025'''' article (July 2025)', 7, 'Year-one Send Network planter in an expensive city; Send planters supplement NAMB''''s declining four-year funding by raising partners and individual supporters, and he is a named planter with national ', 'hunter:church-planters', 'pending', '{"h": "church-planters", "src": "https://www.baptistpress.com/resource-library/news/church-planting-class-of-2025-marks-highest-number-of-new-plants-sinc"}'::jsonb),('Faith Free Wi