ruary 2024 (''''On the ground and running!'''')', 8, 'Young support-raised family early in first term with US (Idaho) donor base and a habit of regular blog updates.', 'hunter:agency-directories', 'pending', '{"h": "agency-directories", "src": "https://blogs.ethnos360.org/travis-lesicka/2024/02/on-the-ground-and-running/"}'::jsonb),('Micah and Laura Myers (Ethnos360)', 'individual', 'expanseofthelight.com', 'Ethnos360 missionaries serving the Lembena people in PNG since 2019; personal ministry blog ''''Expanse of the Light'''' with about/contact/blog pages; supported by Lake Tapps Community Church (WA). | Field: Papua New Guinea (Lembena people) | Comms: Blog updates on expanseofthelight.com (last date verified in search: Nov 2020; s', 7, 'Support-raised tribal church-planting family with own-domain donor blog and visible US church/individual supporter base.', 'hunter:agency-directories', 'pending', '{"h": "agency-directories", "src": "https://expanseofthelight.com/blog/"}'::jsonb),('Dwayne and Rhonda Emberson (Wycliffe Bible Translators USA)', 'individual', 'wycliffe.org/partner/GlowingEmbers', 'Wycliffe members since 1995; Dwayne is a web developer/sysadmin managing Scripture-progress data systems on AWS; Rhonda in children''''s ministry and caregiving. Personal Wycliffe partner/giving page and church partner page at CrossPoint Church. | Field: USA (remote tech role) | Comms: Wycliffe partner page + CrossPoint Church missions page (current; exact date not', 7, 'US-based, fully support-raised Wycliffe couple with personal giving page; tech-oriented and likely receptive to donor software.', 'hunter:agency-directories', 'pending', '{"h": "agency-directories", "src": "https://www.wycliffe.org/partner/GlowingEmbers"}'::jsonb),('Bill and Kathy Brittain (ABWE)', 'individual', 'give.abwe.org/worker/bill-and-kathy-brittain', 'ABWE missionaries to Liberia with an individual worker giving page on ABWE''''s give platform. | Field: Liberia | Comms: Giving page live (no dated n