}'::jsonb),('Layton Smith (Sumterville Free Will Baptist church plant)', 'individual', 'fwbnam.com/category/church-planter/florida', 'Layton and Stephanie Smith are lead planters of a brand-new Free Will Baptist church plant in Sumterville, FL, a joint project between FWBNAM and the Florida State Mission Board. | Field: Sumterville, Florida | Comms: FWBNAM Florida planter page and July 2025 directory', 8, 'Brand-new plant whose planter family must raise monthly individual-donor support under FWBNAM''''s faith-promise model; named planters with a denominational-network profile page and update stream.', 'hunter:church-planters', 'pending', '{"h": "church-planters", "src": "https://fwbnam.com/category/church-planter/florida/"}'::jsonb),('Josh Bennett (Awaken Church (Tifton plant))', 'individual', 'fwbnam.com/category/church-planter/georgia', 'Josh and Ashley Bennett lead Awaken FWB Church, a Free Will Baptist joint-project plant with the State of Georgia, supported by associate planters Shane and Jamie Suggs. | Field: Tifton, Georgia | Comms: FWBNAM Georgia planter page and July 2025 directory', 7, 'Lead planter family raising monthly support from individual donors under FWBNAM''''s support-based planter model; named planters with network profile pages.', 'hunter:church-planters', 'pending', '{"h": "church-planters", "src": "https://fwbnam.com/category/church-planter/georgia/"}'::jsonb),('Shane Suggs (Awaken Church (Tifton plant) — associate planters)', 'individual', 'fwbnam.com/suggs', 'Shane and Jamie Suggs are associate church planters at Awaken FWB Church in Tifton, GA, joint-project workers with FWBNAM and the Georgia state mission board, covering leadership development, operations, and children''''s ministry. | Field: Tifton, Georgia | Comms: FWBNAM personal planter page (fwbnam.com/suggs), 2025', 7, 'Associate planter family with their own FWBNAM support page raising monthly individual-donor faith-promise support — a second distinct donor-communication account within the same plant.', 'hunter:church-planters', 'pending', '{"h": "church-planters", "src": "https://www.fwbnam.com/suggs/"}'::jsonb),('Noah Toney (Redemption Church Beckley)', 'individual', 'noahtoney.substack.com', 'Noah and Cheyanne Toney moved from Greenville, SC to Beckley, WV in 2020 and planted Redemption Church (born August 2021); Noah writes the ''''Almost Heaven: Church Planting Newsletter'''' on Substack covering the plant and pastoral training work. | Field: Beckley, West Virginia | Comms: Substack ''''Almost Heaven'''' church planting newsletter (2025)', 6, 'Support-raised planter in an under-churched, low-income region with an active personal donor newsletter; slightly past year 3 but still communicating with outside supporters, so a warm though not perf', 'hunter:church-planters', 'pending', '{"h": "church-planters", "src": "https://noahtoney.substack.com/p/almost-heaven-planting-newsletter"}'::jsonb),('Samuel Copeland (New church plant with Chicago West Bible Church)', 'individual', 'chicagowest.church', 'The Copeland family moved from Virginia to Chicago in summer 2024 to plant a new Christ-centered, disciple-making, multiethnic church in partnership with Chicago West Bible Church (a NAMB-partnered plant in the Austin community). | Field: Austin / West Side, Chicago, Illinois | Comms: Partner-church church-planting pages describing the Copelands'''' move and support ', 7, 'Planting family relocated cross-country and supported through prayer and financial partnerships with out-of-state churches (Calvary Church, Deer Creek Church) and their members — individual-donor supp', 'hunter:church-planters', 'pending', '{"h": "church-planters", "src": "https://www.yourcalvary.church/chicago"}'::jsonb),('Kenneth Gray (Citizens Church (West Gastonia plant))', 'individual', 'thechapel.life/churchplanting', 'Kenneth Gray planted Citizens Church in West Gastonia, NC in 2025, supported through partner-church church-planting pipelines (The Chapel, Akron''''s church planting partnerships). | Field: West Gastonia, North Carolina | Comms: Partner church planting page listing the 2025 plant (2025)', 7, 'Launch-year planter (2025) named on partner-church giving/planting pages; plants at this stage raise outside support from partner churches'''' members and individual donors.', 'hunter:church-planters', 'pending', '{"h": "church-planters", "src": "https://www.thechapel.life/churchplanting"}'::jsonb),('Matt & Alyssa Harris (Mission Aviation Fellowship)', 'individual', 'maf.org/missionaries/harris', 'Matt is an aircraft maintenance inspector and manager of maintenance training for MAF Papua; Alyssa oversees the MAF Sentani Guesthouse. Full support-raised MAF career missionaries with a dedicated ministry-support giving fund. | Field: Sentani, Papua, Indonesia | Comms: Live personal giving page on give.maf.org (active 2025-2026); newsletter cadence', 9, 'Classic MAF specialist family raising 100% personal support with a live personal giving page on give.maf.org and a US donor base.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://maf.org/missionaries/harris/"}'::jsonb),('Jacob & Audrey Miller (Mission Aviation Fellowship)', 'individual', 'maf.org/miller', 'Jacob is an MAF flight instructor and IT support specialist training missionary pilots; Audrey homeschools their three children. Formerly served with MAF affiliate Asas de Socorro in Brazil. | Field: North Carolina, USA (previously Brazil/M | Comms: Live ministry-support fund page on give.maf.org; personal page current as of 202', 8, 'Support-raised MAF family with a personal MAF page and dedicated giving fund; US-based donor communication is central to their ministry.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://www.maf.org/miller"}'::jsonb),('Erick & Joanna Paradizo (Mission Aviation Fellowship)', 'individual', 'give.maf.org/s/fund/a0e6Q00000Hmw0iQAB/8209-erick-and-joanna-paradizo-ministry-support', 'Erick serves as instructor pilot and Director of Safety at MAF HQ, training new missionary pilots headed overseas. Support-raised career MAF staff couple. | Field: MAF Headquarters, Nampa, Idaho | Comms: Live personal giving fund on give.maf.org (active 2025-2026)', 8, 'Raises full personal support from individual donors with an active MAF ministry-support giving page.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://give.maf.org/s/fund/a0e6Q00000Hmw0iQAB/8209-erick-and-joanna-paradizo-ministry-support"}'::jsonb),('Craig & Ruth Goodman (Mission Aviation Fellowship)', 'individual', 'give.maf.org/s/fund/a0e6Q00000HmvpJQAR/9402-craig-and-ruth-goodman-ministry-support', 'Craig is an aircraft maintenance specialist and Aircraft Helpdesk Supervisor coordinating maintenance support for MAF''''s overseas fleet. Long-term support-raised MAF couple. | Field: MAF Headquarters, Nampa, Idaho | Comms: Live personal giving fund on give.maf.org (active 2025-2026)', 7, 'Career MAF missionaries funded by individual ministry partners, with a live personal giving fund page.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://give.maf.org/s/fund/a0e6Q00000HmvpJQAR/9402-craig-and-ruth-goodman-ministry-support"}'::jsonb),('Brian & Pam Behal (Mission Aviation Fellowship)', 'individual', 'maf.org/behal', 'MAF missionaries since 1993 (Mexico, Ecuador, US mobilization); Brian now serves as a Waypoints Prefield Mentor coaching new MAF missionaries through support raising. Supported by churches like Valley Bible Church Radford. | Field: Virginia, USA (MAF Waypoints prefield me | Comms: Live ministry-support fund page on give.maf.org; listed on supporting-church mis', 7, '30+ year support-raised MAF couple with personal MAF page and giving fund; deeply embedded in the support-raising world DonorSend serves.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://www.maf.org/behal"}'::jsonb),('John & Marilyn Gorenflo (Mission Aviation Fellowship)', 'individual', 'g