ng Papua New Guineans translating Scripture, song books, literacy and Sunday school materials into Tiaang; keeps a personal WordPress blog ''''A New Heart in PNG'''' plus a Wycliffe partner giving page. | Field: Papua New Guinea (Tiaang language, New I | Comms: Personal blog anewheartinpng.wordpress.com plus live Wycliffe partner page; late', 9, 'Single support-raised Wycliffe translator with both a personal blog and a personal giving page — ideal donor-communication profile.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://www.wycliffe.org/partner/JessieWright"}'::jsonb),('Kendall & Renee Isaac (Wycliffe Bible Translators)', 'individual', 'wycliffe.org/partner/IsaacFamily', 'Wycliffe missionary family with a dedicated partner/giving page (wycliffe.org/partner/IsaacFamily). | Field: Wycliffe (assignment not verified) | Comms: Live Wycliffe partner/giving page (2025-2026)', 7, 'Support-raised Wycliffe members with a live personal giving page for individual donors.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://www.wycliffe.org/partner/IsaacFamily"}'::jsonb),('Michelle Foster (Wycliffe Bible Translators)', 'individual', 'wycliffe.org/partner/mjfoster', 'Individual Wycliffe missionary with a personal partner/giving page on wycliffe.org. | Field: Wycliffe (linguistics/translation suppor | Comms: Live Wycliffe partner/giving page (2025-2026)', 7, 'Single support-raised Wycliffe member with personal giving page and individual-donor support base.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://www.wycliffe.org/partner/mjfoster"}'::jsonb),('Carle & Vicky Gustavison (Wycliffe Bible Translators)', 'individual', 'wycliffe.org/partner/Bibles', 'Wycliffe couple with a personal partner/giving page on wycliffe.org. | Field: Wycliffe (Scripture access ministry) | Comms: Live Wycliffe partner/giving page (2025-2026)', 7, 'Support-raised Wycliffe members funded by individual donors via a personal giving page.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://www.wycliffe.org/partner/Bibles"}'::jsonb),('John Marselus (JAARS)', 'individual', 'jaars.org/staff-support?fund-code=John+Marselus+102192', 'JAARS aviation staff member with a named staff-support fund; JAARS supported staff build teams of ministry partners who fund their living and ministry expenses. | Field: JAARS base, Waxhaw, North Carolina (miss | Comms: Live JAARS staff-support giving page with personal fund code (2025-2026)', 7, 'Named JAARS supported-staff giving page confirms partnership-development funding model with individual donors.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://www.jaars.org/staff-support?fund-code=John+Marselus+102192"}'::jsonb)
