('Peter & Emily Goodwin (World Gospel Mission)', 'individual', 'wgm.org/missionary/goodwin', 'Peter is a vitreoretinal surgeon and Emily a pediatric hematologist-oncologist serving long-term at Tenwek Mission Hospital after two one-year terms; WGM missionaries raise full personal support with online giving pages. | Field: Tenwek Hospital, Bomet, Kenya | Comms: Live WGM missionary profile/giving page (2025-2026); newsletter date not verifie', 9, 'Specialist medical missionary couple, individually support-raised through WGM with a personal missionary giving page.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://wgm.org/missionary/goodwin"}'::jsonb),('Jonathan Steen & Meghan Murphy-Steen (World Gospel Mission)', 'individual', 'wgm.org/missionary/steen', 'Jonathan (family medicine) teaches in the Tenwek Family Medicine Residency; Meghan is an OB-GYN heading Tenwek''''s Ob/Gyn department. Support-raised WGM global workers. | Field: Tenwek Hospital, Bomet, Kenya | Comms: Live WGM missionary profile/giving page (2025-2026)', 9, 'Dual-physician missionary couple raising personal support through WGM with a personal giving page and US donor base.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://wgm.org/missionary/steen"}'::jsonb),('Russ & Beth White (World Gospel Mission)', 'individual', 'wgm.org/missionary/white', 'WGM missionary couple with a personal missionary profile and giving page on wgm.org, surfaced in Tenwek medical missions context. | Field: Kenya (WGM medical/ministry, Tenwek-conn | Comms: Live WGM missionary profile/giving page (2025-2026)', 7, 'Support-raised WGM missionaries funded by individual donors via personal giving page.', 'hunter:specialists', 'pending', '{"h": "specialists", "src": "https://wgm.org/missionary/white"}'::jsonb),('Eric & Rachel McLaughlin (Serge)', 'individual', 'give.serge.org/donate/eric-and-rachel-mclaughlin', 'Eric (family medicine) and Rachel (OB-GYN) are founding ''''McCropder'''' phys