signate gifts to specific staff. | Field: USA (Executive Director, frontier mission mobilization) | Comms: Unknown date — active staff profile and staff-designated giving page', 7, 'Support-raised staff with designated personal giving option on frontierfellowship.com/give.', 'hunter:agencies2', 'pending', '{"h": "agencies2", "src": "https://frontierfellowship.com/staff-directory-ethan-collins/"}'::jsonb),('Dan McNerney (Frontier Fellowship)', 'individual', 'frontierfellowship.com/staff-directory-dan-mcnerney', 'Senior Associate at Frontier Fellowship mobilizing churches toward unreached peoples. | Field: USA (Senior Associate) | Comms: Unknown date — active staff profile and staff-designated giving page', 6, 'Support-raised staffer; donors can designate gifts to him via the org give page.', 'hunter:agencies2', 'pending', '{"h": "agencies2", "src": "https://frontierfellowship.com/staff-directory-dan-mcnerney/"}'::jsonb),('Tara Taylor (Frontier Fellowship)', 'individual', 'frontierfellowship.com/staff-directory-tara-taylor', 'Frontier Fellowship staff member with public profile; staff gifts designated via org give page. | Field: USA | Comms: Unknown date — active staff profile and staff-designated giving page', 6, 'Support-raised staffer with designated personal giving option.', 'hunter:agencies2', 'pending', '{"h": "agencies2", "src": "https://frontierfellowship.com/staff-directory-tara-taylor/"}'::jsonb),('Bradley Long (Frontier Fellowship)', 'individual', 'frontierfellowship.com/staff-directory-bradley-long', 'Associate Director at Frontier Fellowship. | Field: USA (Associate Director) | Comms: Unknown date — active staff profile and staff-designated giving page', 6, 'Support-raised staffer with designated personal giving option on org give page.', 'hunter:agencies2', 'pending', '{"h": "agencies2", "src": "https://frontierfellowship.com/staff-directory-bradley-long/"}'::jsonb),('Philana Cunningham (Frontier Fellowship)', 'individual', 'frontierfellowship.com/cunningham', 'Frontier Fellowship staff member with public profile page. | Field: USA | Comms: Unknown date — active staff profile and staff-designated giving page', 6, 'Support-raised staffer with designated personal giving option on org give page.', 'hunter:agencies2', 'pending', '{"h": "agencies2", "src": "https://frontierfellowship.com/cunningham/"}'::jsonb),('George & Pamela Pendergrass (Frontier Fellowship)', 'individual', 'frontierfellowship.com/staff', 'Associate Directors at Frontier Fellowship listed on the staff directory. | Field: USA (Associate Directors) | Comms: Unknown date — listed on current staff directory with designated giving option', 6, 'Support-raised couple; donors can designate gifts to them via the org give page.', 'hunter:agencies2', 'pending', '{"h": "agencies2", "src": "https://frontierfellowship.com/staff/"}'::jsonb),('Chad & Noriko Snow (TEAM)', 'individual', 'team.org/people/chad-snow', 'TEAM missionary with a personal people/giving page; met Noriko in Japan and serves in church ministry there. | Field: Japan | Comms: Unknown date — active team.org missionary profile/giving page', 8, 'Named TEAM missionary with a personal team.org profile/giving page; TEAM workers raise personal support.', 'hunter:agencies2', 'pending', '{"h": "agencies2", "src": "https://team.org/people/chad-snow/"}'::jsonb),('Chris & Rosalie Duryee (ABWE)', 'individual', 'rosalieduryeewrites.substack.com', 'ABWE missionaries to Spain in an active support-raising push; their ''''Goals'''' post sets targets of 30% of support by end of December and 50% by February, noting they are drawing on savings until they hit 50%. Recently wrote about their commissioning service. | Field: Guadalajara area, Castilla-La Mancha, Spain (church planting | Comms: Substack posts (goals/commissioning), 2026; monthly email update', 9, 'ABWE couple publicly posting support percentages and deadlines — actively building/rebuilding a US individual donor base this moment.', 'hunter:appointees', 'pending', '{"h": "appointees", "src": "https://rosalieduryeewrites.substack.com/p/goals"}'::jsonb),('Juan Gutierrez (FBMI)', 'individual', 'fbmi.org/prayer-letters/juan-gutierrez-prayer-letter-on-the-deputation-trail', 'FBMI missionary to Honduras on deputation, currently at 12% of needed support (prayer letter dated July 12, 2026); traveling coast to coast (CA, KS, TX, VA, WI, OH, NJ) with nearly all 2026 Sundays booked and 2027 meetings being scheduled. | Field: Honduras | Comms: FBMI prayer letter (email/web), July 12, 2026', 9, 'Early-stage deputation (12%) with years of donor-base building ahead — ideal timing for a donor CRM/texting tool.', 'hunter:appointees', 'pending', '{"h": "appointees", "src": "https://fbmi.org/prayer-letters/juan-gutierrez-prayer-letter-on-the-deputation-trail"}'::jsonb),('Abram Gomez (FBMI)', 'individual', 'fbmi.org/prayer-letters/abram-gomez-prayer-letter-blessed-meetings-and-ministries', 'FBMI missionary finishing deputation; July 11, 2026 letter asks prayer to reach 100% of support in time to leave for the field by October 12. In the final sprint of donor-base building. | Field: (FBMI field — see prayer letters) | Comms: FBMI prayer letter (email/web), July 11, 2026', 8, 'Weeks from departure — converting his deputation contacts into a permanent donor base right now; prime moment to adopt donor comms tooling.', 'hunter:appointees', 'pending', '{"h": "appointees", "src": "https://fbmi.org/prayer-letters/abram-gomez-prayer-letter-blessed-meetings-and-ministries"}'::jsonb),('Anna Long (FBMI)', 'individual', 'fbmi.org/prayer-letters/anna-long-prayer-letter-deputation-travels', 'Single missionary on deputation with FBMI''''s Team Thailand, traveling to supporting churches and publishing ''''Deputation Travels'''' prayer letters in 2026. | Field: Thailand (Team Thailand) | Comms: FBMI prayer letter (email/web), 2026', 8, 'Pre-field, actively raising personal support from US churches and individuals for Thailand.', 'hunter:appointees', 'pending', '{"h": "appointees", "src": "https://fbmi.org/prayer-letters/anna-long-prayer-letter-deputation-travels"}'::jsonb),('Flynn & Lily Ginino (FBMI)', 'individual', 'fbmi.org/prayer-letters/flynn-and-lily-ginino-prayer-letter-deputation-travels', 'Couple on deputation for Papua New Guinea; traveled 7,500+ miles across 9 states since January 2026 meeting pastors and churches, with schedule openings still to fill and churches taking them on for support. | Field: Papua New Guinea | Comms: FBMI prayer letter (email/web), 2026', 8, 'Mid-deputation couple actively adding supporting churches/individuals — building the donor list DonorSend would manage.', 'hunter:appointees', 'pending', '{"h": "appointees", "src": "https://fbmi.org/prayer-letters/flynn-and-lily-ginino-prayer-letter-deputation-travels"}'::jsonb),('Dustin & Hilda Schurg (FBMI)', 'individual', 'fbmi.org/prayer-letters/dustin-and-hilda-schurg-prayer-letter-moving-forward-by-faith', 'Family on deputation for Panama, asking prayer for safe travels ''''to finish deputation''''; May/June 2026 letter describes a full travel schedule with young children and a pregnancy. | Field: Panama | Comms: FBMI prayer letter (email/web), ~July 2026 (May–June recap)', 8, 'In the closing stretch of support raising for Panama — high urgency to organize and communicate with new donors.', 'hunter:appointees', 'pending', '{"h": "appointees", "src": "https://fbmi.org/prayer-letters/dustin-and-hilda-schurg-prayer-letter-moving-forward-by-faith"}'::jsonb)
