('Jared & Tiffany Stalnaker (FBMI)', 'individual', 'fbmi.org/prayer-letters/jared-and-tiffany-stalnaker-prayer-letter-grateful-hearts-the-end-of-the-beginning', 'Couple who just reached 100% of needed support in 2026 (''''The End of the Beginning'''') after deputation, with newborn twins; now transitioning from deputation to departure. | Field: (FBMI field — see prayer letters) | Comms: FBMI prayer letter (email/web), 2026', 6, 'Just fully funded — needs to onboard and retain a brand-new donor base as they head to the field; slightly past peak urgency.', 'hunter:appointees', 'pending', '{"h": "appointees", "src": "https://fbmi.org/prayer-letters/jared-and-tiffany-stalnaker-prayer-letter-grateful-hearts-the-end-of-the-beginning"}'::jsonb),('The Matsuda Family (Independent Baptist, sent under Faith Baptist Church, Huanuco)', 'individual', 'thematsudafamily.com', 'Missionary family (5 years serving in Arequipa, Peru) on a months-long 2026 US deputation tour to raise support, adding partner churches like Citrus Baptist (Inverness, FL), Unity Baptist (Winston-Salem, NC), and Temple Baptist (Arcadia, FL); welcomed a baby mid-tour. | Field: Arequipa, Peru | Comms: Blog deputation updates at thematsudafamily.com, 2026', 8, 'Classic furlough/deputation rebuild: actively traveling the US now to grow their US donor base for return to Peru.', 'hunter:appointees', 'pending', '{"h": "appointees", "src": "https://thematsudafamily.com/our-missionary-deputation-journey/"}'::jsonb),('Emilee Coffey (Vision Baptist Missions)', 'individual', 'projectsouthafrica.com', 'New Vision Baptist Missions helps missionary to South Africa (age 23, daughter of VBM missionaries Mark & Amy Coffey) who has just begun deputation after two years on the VBM home office staff. | Field: South Africa (helps ministry) | Comms: Prayer letters via Project South Africa site / VBM Instagram announcement, 2026', 8, 'Newly announced appointee at the very start of deputation — building her personal US donor base fr